---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Software Dev</h2>
		<p>I specialize in human-centered design frontend work, with professional experience across the whole stack: React, Vue, Django, PostgreSQL, harness.js, fastAPI, AWS, and Docker products. I have additional experience with Databricks, Azure, R + tidyverse, highcharts, D3.js, and Python in a data visualization and analysis context, and experience with Svelte in a journalism context.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Hobbies</h2>
		<p>Music and dance are a huge part of my life, producing and mixing music as a DJ since 2021, and I have been dancing in some capacity since I was a kid! Outside of those, my other hobbies include cooking, hiking, and being a dog dad for my boy, Biko. Picked up a new camera in 2026 and documenting that journey here, and currently learning how to play hockey!</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Data Science and AI</h2>
		<p>I am interested in the impact of data science and artificial intelligence for the public good, learning about the capabilities of generative AI and continually seeking ways to utilize generative AI ethically and responsibly in workflows that center the worker. Human Autonomy Centered, Open-source Oriented, Science for Public Good.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_65);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
